If clinicians are recording the process of request and provision of medical devices, then this summary should be derived from those recordings, to ensure that there is no duplication of clinical input. (en)">
			misuse = <"Brukes ikke for å rekvirere høreapparat - Bruk INSTRUCTION.request arketypene for dette formålet.

